::The Oblitercons::

The Oblitercons get out of the CR chambers, Dark One walking to the closest 
console to check on scans. He frowns. There was a new pod nearby .... with 
Predacons near it!

"Follow me," he says to his group, walking out of the base and flying off. 
THe rest of the Oblitercons follow on foot, running into the forest.
